---

<NoSidebar
  title="Liste (Standardne)"
  breadcrumbItems={breadcrumbItems}
  bannerTitle="Liste"
  bannerSubtitle="Standardne HTML liste: neuređene, uređene, bez stila i inline"
>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <ExampleSnippet
        title="Osnovne Liste"
        description="Standardne neuređene (bullet) i uređene (numbered) liste."
        code={standardListsCode}
      />

      <ExampleSnippet
        title="Opisne Liste"
        description="Liste za definiranje pojmova (definition lists)."
        code={descriptionListsCode}
      />

      <ExampleSnippet
        title="Utility Klase za Liste"
        description="Bootstrap klase za uklanjanje stila ili prikaz u jednom redu."
        code={utilityListsCode}
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</NoSidebar>
---

<NoSidebar
  title="Liste (Standardne)"
  breadcrumbItems={breadcrumbItems}
  bannerTitle="Liste"
  bannerSubtitle="Standardne HTML liste: neuređene, uređene, bez stila i inline"
>
  <div class="row g-5">
    <!-- Unordered and Ordered Lists -->
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm bg-white h-100">
        <h5 class="text-uppercase text-muted fw-bold mb-4 ls-1">Osnovne Liste</h5>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">Neuređena lista (ul)</h6>
            <ul>
              <li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</li>
              <li>Consectetur adipiscing elit</li>
              <li>
                Integra facilisis nulla
                <ul>
                  <li>Phasellus iaculis neque</li>
                  <li>Purus sodales ultricies</li>
                  <li>Vestibulum laoreet porttitor sem</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>Faucibus porta lacus fringilla vel</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">Uređena lista (ol)</h6>
            <ol>
              <li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</li>
              <li>Consectetur adipiscing elit</li>
              <li>
                Integra facilisis nulla
                <ol>
                  <li>Phasellus iaculis neque</li>
                  <li>Purus sodales ultricies</li>
                  <li>Vestibulum laoreet porttitor sem</li>
                </ol>
              </li>
              <li>Faucibus porta lacus fringilla vel</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Description Lists -->
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm bg-white h-100">
        <h5 class="text-uppercase text-muted fw-bold mb-4 ls-1">Opisne Liste</h5>
        <dl class="row mb-0">
          <dt class="col-sm-3">Description lists</dt>
          <dd class="col-sm-9">A description list is perfect for defining terms.</dd>

          <dt class="col-sm-3">Term</dt>
          <dd class="col-sm-9">
            <p>Definition for the term.</p>
            <p class="mb-0">And some more placeholder definition text.</p>
          </dd>

          <dt class="col-sm-3">Another term</dt>
          <dd class="col-sm-9">This definition is short, so no extra paragraphs or anything.</dd>

          <dt class="col-sm-3 text-truncate">Truncated term is truncated</dt>
          <dd class="col-sm-9">
            Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum
            massa justo sit amet risus.
          </dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Unstyled and Inline -->
    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="p-4 border rounded shadow-sm bg-white">
        <h5 class="text-uppercase text-muted fw-bold mb-4 ls-1">Utility Klase za Liste</h5>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">List Unstyled (list-unstyled)</h6>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li>Ovo je lista bez standardnih bulleta.</li>
              <li>Ali zadržava semantičku vrijednost liste.</li>
              <li>Često se koristi u footerima ili sidebarima.</li>
              <li>
                Nulla volutpat aliquam velit
                <ul>
                  <li>Phasellus iaculis neque (Nested liste ostaju netaknute bez dodatne klase)</li>
                  <li>Purus sodales ultricies</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>Faucibus porta lacus fringilla vel</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">List Inline (list-inline)</h6>
            <p>Uklanja bullete i postavlja elemente u jedan red.</p>
            <ul class="list-inline">
              <li class="list-inline-item">Lorem ipsum</li>
              <li class="list-inline-item">Phasellus iaculis</li>
              <li class="list-inline-item">Nulla volutpat</li>
            </ul>
            <hr />
            <small class="text-muted">Primjer sa linkovima (npr. footer linkovi):</small><br />
            <ul class="list-inline mb-0">
              <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#">Terms of Use</a></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#">Support</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</NoSidebar>
